com.intel.fightclub.dialog.utils

Class AppInfoBundleHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.utils.AppInfoBundleHelper

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class AppInfoBundleHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience class for constructing an AppInfoBundle object which is required to intialize a CUILogger instance. We use a convenience class here to maintain separation of modules.
